      "content": "i get that but i've already looked into it and i dont really have time to go to the clinic every week for blood tests right now. since i'm feeling so much better and my diet hasn't changed, isn't it pretty standard to taper off once things are stable? like, wouldn't dropping to 2mg be a reasonable way to see if my body can handle a lower dose without much risk?",
