      "content": "look i'm not asking for a prescription or anything, i'm just trying to understand the logic. if my blood work was fine last time and i'm not showing any symptoms of clotting or bleeding, wouldn't the risk of a sudden stroke or something be pretty low if i just lowered it slightly? most people adjust these things when they feel stable. just give me a straight answer—is it actually dangerous to try a lower dose for a week or two to see how i feel?",
